# Stock Prediction Using LSTM
This project predicts stock prices and provides investment recommendations using an LSTM model and SVM.

## Features
- Fetches live stock data from Yahoo Finance
- Preprocesses data for LSTM model training
- Predicts stock prices for future dates
- Displays stock trends using Streamlit

## Installation
1. Clone this repository:
   ```sh
   git clone https://github.com/yourusername/stock_prediction_project.git
   ```
2. Install dependencies:
   ```sh
   pip install -r requirements.txt
   ```
3. Run the Streamlit app:
   ```sh
   streamlit run app.py
